# Auto Build & Package After Changes

After editing any `.ts` file under `src/` or `package.json`, always run the extension build and generate the VSIX:

```bash
cd /Users/hari-19343/Zide-vscode && npm run build && npx @vscode/vsce package --no-dependencies
```

Verify both steps exit with code 0. If the build fails, fix the errors before proceeding.
